Oh no! Your web browser is out of date

How to upgrade your browser:

  • Use your "system update" or "software update" feature of your OS or device
  • Alternatively, install a new browser such as Firefox, or Chrome
  • It's most likely you need to upgrade to use Loomio, but, if you think you're seeing this message in error, proceed to Loomio with your current browser.

Stuck? Email contact@loomio.org for support.
